				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-T%E1%BB%AD-Ngang/C%E1%BA%A3m-ng%E1%BB%99-k%E1%BB%B3-20/poem-H5YA0TL7lRbnfJqG7nExKg">Cảm ngộ kỳ 20 - 感遇其二十</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-T%E1%BB%AD-Ngang/author-KAeplXpuQBYC4UQBLqb_RQ">Trần Tử Ngang</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-K%E1%BB%B3/%C4%90%E1%BB%89nh-Minh-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-tb-mZVQzlQRzQhoKGz3MrQ">Đỉnh Minh tự - 鼎銘寺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-K%E1%BB%B3/author-w6Nzdd7lvpiIacUaKAMQvw">Nguyễn Kỳ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%C3%A1o/%C4%90%E1%BB%99-quan-san/poem-AacgT9F2TQnbuMwMeO8faw">Độ quan san - 度關山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%C3%A1o/author-eKAWfrr_7bNBR5FBbe19qg">Tào Tháo</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/L%C3%BD-M%E1%BA%ADt-tr%E1%BA%A7n-t%C3%ACnh-bi%E1%BB%83u/poem-0BeSN4In5c5TT58DpTZQJQ">Lý Mật trần tình biểu - 李密陳情表</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/Ngh%C4%A9-%C4%90%C3%A0m-Th%E1%BA%BF-Ph%E1%BB%95-h%E1%BA%A1-V%C3%A2n-C%E1%BB%91c-c%E1%BB%AD-nh%C3%A2n/poem-FBEC-jvV6ASxRMb9J9z-vQ">Nghĩ Đàm Thế Phổ hạ Vân Cốc cử nhân - 擬譚世溥夏雲谷舉人</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/author-h3EvqeQvlQUxq2sceUWWYQ">Đoàn Huyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BA%A1i-%C3%8Dch-Quy/Nguy%C3%AAn-nh%E1%BA%ADt-tri%E1%BB%81u-h%E1%BB%99i/poem-wfLSGSJQAgt0ngj9lMxYZQ">Nguyên nhật triều hội - 元日朝會</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BA%A1i-%C3%8Dch-Quy/author-jxffn0kiYqR6Jxsac5acdA">Lại Ích Quy</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/Nh%C3%A0n-v%E1%BB%8Bnh-k%E1%BB%B3-04/poem-cTtqLXRrcdoXbZp5CaRFsQ">Nhàn vịnh kỳ 04 - 間詠其四</a> (<a hr